<span id="freeTextContainer12069288336799160071">(I wrote this in sleepy conditions..)<br/>Right Review here: <a href='www.bookaapi.com/book-review/clear-light-of-day-by-anita-desai/' rel='nofollow noopener'>www.bookaapi.com/book-review/clear-light-of-day-by-anita-desai/</a><br/><br/>The book is divided in 4 parts. First part and the last part is of present and the middle two were of past.<br/><br/>The story is of 4 siblings. Bimla, Tara, Raja and Baba (special care).<br/>When Tara come back to India, she finds Bim living a very low life. <br/>Bim was the eldest of the one and she has to take care of the others after her parents death. While doing so, she forgets to herself. Sh</span>
